body:
It may be helpful， In my code, I find that tensorflow/tensorflow/cc/saved_model/loader.cc, ReadBinaryProto load saved_model.pb 。
The model is loaded in the SavedModel  way, but My model is format MetaGraphDef .
you can see [SavedModel ](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/core/protobuf/saved_model.proto#L20)
